snippet.title: FlatSoccer - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
FlatSoccer is an online multiplayer soccer game for Windows and Android. Have fun with your friends in fun and competitive football matches, compete with players from all over the world in a world ranking by seasons.

*Buy Game for Windows:* https://www.vaneltongamedev.com/flatsoccer
*Play free on Android:* https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vgd.flatsoccer

♦ *Voices:*
- Thinksojoe
- Renato Mapelli
- Bianca Wolski

♦ *Social and Website:*
- Website: https://vaneltongamedev.com
- Instagram: @VaneltonGamedev

♦ *Licenses:*
Song: JJD - Adventure [NCS Release]
Music provided by NoCopyrightSounds
Free Download/Stream: http://ncs.io/adventure
Watch: http://youtu.be/f2xGxd9xPYA
